  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Let's light a candle... it's the beginning of Sparky's great adventure!</h2>The Sparky's battlefield is the only 6 x 12 square lattices.<br>Make an efficient route for Sparky in this new challenging puzzle.<br><br>This game is lighting a candle by leading Sparky. All you can do is planting a flag on the route as a destination.<br>Sparky will find its way to shortest distance, but you should know Sparky's impulse very much... <br>Try to find the best route for each stage!<br><br>Route Candle has more than 100 stages and the various obstacles don't get you boring.<br><br>Find your own enjoys!<br><br><br>Twitter @peakvox / @peakvox_en",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Let's light a candle... it's the beginning of Sparky's great adventure!</h2>The Sparky's battlefield is the only 6 x 12 square lattices.<br>Make an efficient route for Sparky in this new challenging puzzle.<br><br>This game is lighting a candle by leading Sparky. All you can do is planting a flag on the route as a destination.<br>Sparky will find its way to shortest distance, but you should know Sparky's impulse very much... <br>Try to find the best route for each stage!<br><br>Route Candle has more than 100 stages and the various obstacles don't get you boring.<br><br>Find your own enjoys!<br><br><br>Twitter @peakvox / @peakvox_en",
